        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.7.2" date="2025-11-11">
      <description translate="no">
        <p>Added</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Allow filtering on all other unit properties</li>
          <li>Add a filter marker on browser column</li>
          <li>Allow string filter to filter on start, end or middle</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Fixed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Column title that removed continuously first letter each time, it stop the issue but
            don't recover the damage</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.6.4" date="2025-11-5">
      <description translate="no">
        <p>Added</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Popup menu reenable option</li>
          <li>Display unit properties dialog shortcut (Ctrl+P)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Fixed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Sorting on user defined unit's property columns wasn't working at initiation time</li>
          <li>UX, extra controls side panel now scrolls</li>
          <li>Unit file path handling</li>
          <li>System unit takes precedence on User Session units</li>
          <li>Unit journal events displayed twice</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>
